text: Mobil 1 Racing may refer to: *Holden Dealer Team - Australian motorsport team that had Mobil as title sponsor from 1985 to 1990 *Advantage Racing - Australian motorsport team that had Mobil as title sponsor in 1992/93 *Walkinshaw Andretti United - Australian motorsport team that had Mobil as title sponsor at various times since 1994 See also Mobil 1#Sponsorships
title: Mobil 1 Racing
